===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[wind]]; to [[tie]]; to [[bind]]; to [[twine]]
#: {{zh-co|纏 著[着]{zhe} 繃帶|to wind bandage; to bandage}}
#: {{zh-x|他 把 毛線 纏 成 球。|He wound the wool yarn into a ball.}}
# to [[tangle]]
#: {{zh-x|那 兩 股 線 怎麼 纏 在一起 了 呢？|How did the two strands of string become entangled?}}
# to [[pester]]; to [[harass]]
#: {{zh-x|你 幹嘛 一直 纏 著[着]{zhe} 我？|Why do you keep pestering me?}}
#* {{quote-song|nan-hbl|year=2014|author=廖偉志|artist=w:zh:蔡佳麟|title=尚痛的記誌|titleurl=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4NDnMGoLEg|album=阿宅的心聲}}
#*: {{zh-q|你 哭 的 模樣 像 惡夢　伴 阮{gún} 夜夜 纏||TW}}
# {{lb|zh|dialectal}} to [[deal with]]
#: {{zh-x|這個 傢伙 很 難 纏。|This fellow is very hard to deal with.}}
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} to be in a [[tangle]]; to get [[entangled]]
#: {{zh-x|代誌 傷{siuⁿ} 濟{chōe}，纏 𣍐{bōe} 直。|There are too many things to do that it's endlessly in a tangle.|MN}} 

